Package com.dhk.controllers

Class WindowController

java.lang.Object
com.dhk.controllers.WindowController
All Implemented Interfaces:
Controller, WindowListener, EventListener
public class WindowController extends Object implements Controller, WindowListener
This class controls the application's window. The window listener is initialized with this class. It defines how often the application window should be refreshed, and it initializes the object that allows the application to be minimized to the system tray and restored from the system tray.
